#, fuzzy
msgid "Activate or deactivate Mongo Clients"
msgstr "Ativar ou desativar os clientes Mongo"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
