#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/mongodb.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If you are using the `quarkus-micrometer`, `quarkus-mongodb-client` can provide metrics about the connection pools.\n"
